            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="accordion-content hidden px-6 py-4">
          <div class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#064161] space-y-4">
            <div class="border-l-4 border-[#FEE96A] pl-4">
             <span class="font-bold text-[#064161]">Jamaica:</span> Small, scrappy studios like Studio One and Treasure Isle made magic with limited gear. Most reggae came from these studios Engineers experimented with reverb-heavy mixes and tape manipulation, laying the groundwork for dub in the following decade.
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center my-2 space-x-2">
              <img src="https://syvkefpljdcoricvmqcy.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/images/carri_assets/content_images/Studio_one.jpeg" alt="Studio One" class="w-64 h-64 rounded-xl object-cover">
